description:
src/lib.rs line 52 calls `aws_config::load_from_env().await`. As of aws-config 1.x this function is `#[deprecated]` in favour of `aws_config::defaults(BehaviorVersion::latest()).load().await`, which makes the SDK behaviour-version pinning explicit and forward-compatible.

Current code:
    let cfg = aws_config::load_from_env().await;

Recommended:
    use aws_config::BehaviorVersion;
    let cfg = aws_config::defaults(BehaviorVersion::latest()).load().await;

This is the same fix as 8bh8.3 for secretx-aws-sm. Both crates should be updated in one pass for consistency.
